      • getName

        public final Name getName(NameType nameType)
        Description copied from interface: Named
        Retrieves a Name that belongs to this Named that is appropriate for the supplied NameType, or null if no such Name can be found.

        Implementations of this method are permitted to return null.

        Specified by:
        getName in interface Named
        Parameters:
        nameType - the NameType for which a Name will be sought; may be null in which case the implementation may decide what kind of Name to return (including null)
        Returns:
        a Name indexed under the supplied NameType, or null

      • isResolveable

        public boolean isResolveable(String name)
        Returns true if name is equal to the value of a NameType that, when passed to Named.getName(NameType), results in a non-null Name, or if subsequent VariableResolvers are able to make sense of the supplied name parameter.
        Specified by:
        isResolveable in interface org.mvel2.integration.VariableResolverFactory
        Parameters:
        name - the value of a NameType; may be null
        Returns:
        true if this NameResolverFactory or any of its chained VariableResolverFactory instances can resolve an MVEL variable of the given name; false otherwise
        See Also:
        VariableResolverFactory, BaseVariableResolverFactory.isNextResolveable(String), VariableResolver, NameResolver

      • createNameResolver

        protected NameResolver createNameResolver(Named named,
                                          String name)
        Creates and returns a NameResolver appropriate for the supplied Named and the supplied value.
        Parameters:
        named - the Named that serves as the virtual universe or domain of Names that are potentially resolvable into NameResolvers vended by this NameResolverFactory; must not be null
        name - the name of the variable the new NameResolver will return from its NameResolver.getName() method; must not be null
        Returns:
        a non-null NameResolver
        Throws:
        IllegalArgumentException - if either named or name is null

        public boolean isTarget(String name)
        Returns true if the supplied name is non-null and this NameResolverFactory has a NameResolver that has been installed by the inner workings of the isResolveable(String) method to resolve a Name indexed under the supplied name.
        Specified by:
        isTarget in interface org.mvel2.integration.VariableResolverFactory
        Parameters:
        name - the value of a NameType; may be null
        Returns:
        true if the supplied name is non-null and this NameResolverFactory has a NameResolver that has been installed by the inner workings of the isResolveable(String) method to resolve a Name indexed under the supplied name; false in all other cases
